overview.en: OXY Token is a token for OxySwap DEX. It is also a token based on DAO. It build DApps with community consensus. And the OxySwap is the first Dapp in OxyDAO.
overview.zh: OXY是去中心化交易所OxySwap的通证，也是以建立DAO(Decentralized Autonomous Organizations)为基础的生态代币，通过构建完备的社区共识，基于社区构建生态交互与应用，Oxyswap是DAO生态的第一个去中心化Defi应用。
